<div class="cheadbg">
    <div class="customhead" style="font-size:40px;">• Age Altering Anomaly •</div>
</div>
{{Blurimage|file=a67dffc675d22242dfff9bceab06a8b6.jpg|caption=New TV huh?|align=right}}
Level 93 is affected by an age-altering anomaly that changes the age of every individual upon entering the level. The anomaly takes effect right away and is unavoidable. The change is completely painless and usually happens so fast that most wanderers might not even notice, except for noticing it after seeing their reflection.

Individuals who were alive during the 1990s will physically appear as they did during that decade. Their height, facial features, hair color, and overall appearance are reverted to match that period of their lives. Clothing are not affected by the anomaly. Also, Memories and personality remain unchanged.

People born after the 1990s are instead assigned a random age, usually between 18 and 55 years old. The assigned age appears to be completely random and may differ with each visit to the level.

The anomaly remains active for the entire duration of one's stay within Level 93. Upon leaving, the wanderer's body immediately returns to its original physical age. The anomaly do not appear to cause any permanent changes, although individuals born after the 1990s may be assigned a different physical age each time they enter.

The anomaly also prevents aging. Individuals remain at the same age until they leave, regardless of how much time passes.
