Level 93 is almost completely devoid of entities. Due to the effects of [[Phenomenon 15]], each individual experiences their own version of the level. No hostile entities have ever been confirmed within Level 93.

The only known entities are pets. If a wanderer owned a cat or dog before entering the level may encounter their pet somewhere within the house. These animals behave normally and are generally friendly toward their owner. They do not show signs of aging while inside the level.

Not every person will encounter their pet. Those who do often report seeing the pet only briefly before it wanders into another room. As it will disappear and reappear elsewhere in the house. The reason for this phenomenon remains unknown.

